{"tid":920392,"cid":21,"subCid":2,"title":"2018黑市音樂","createTime":"2018-11-28T19:32:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T14:11:11.000Z","uid":192257,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d339afbf0372b457a1f81512bdcfce81efd68ff0","tid":920392,"uid":192257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T19:32:29.000Z","msg":"見冇人開又訓唔著我就9up下啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p3nyk8b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp3nyk8b.png&h=12d36789&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n數隊來自台灣的地下樂隊會係12月份會到香港HA搞show，氣氛好好架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<strong>我極力推薦孔雀眼同Hello Nico </strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jN3iCNMjIpQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjN3iCNMjIpQ&d=BEUgg9UfG23NtCXPAgLaf9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=0a5cd667\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jN3iCNMjIpQ</a><br />\n<br />\n(Verse)可是你的自卑勝過了一切愛你的人於是你把你的愛人們都殺死了 <br />\n<br />\n細心嘅朋友會發現佢同草東沒有派對嘅鬼歌詞係相同的。 孔雀眼 JADE EYES主唱令晴正正就是草東的創團成員！你可以係佢地作品入面搵到草東早期的dancepunk身影，同時係Synthesizer上既運用亦將佢地變成曯目既迷幻New Wave樂隊，如果你鐘意草東，你都一定會鐘意孔雀眼！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tKO7AiQ4f8I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtKO7AiQ4f8I&d=BEUgg9UfG23NtCXPAgLaf9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=4c8d6cfd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tKO7AiQ4f8I</a><br />\n<br />\n你該是最了解你的人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Hello Nico現場感染力係大到想哭 聽到好虐心</strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2018 黑市私會 香港站 @ Hidden Agenda<br />\n「黑市音樂與朋友們年度私密聚會」<br />\n12/22（週六）下午 1800-2300 五小時音樂會<br />\nHello Nico / 孔雀眼 JADE EYES / 椰子!! Coconuts / 皇后皮箱 QueenSuitcase / D O W N E R<br />\n預售 HKD 400 / 二人同行 HKD 700<br />\n*預售票滿將不開放現場票<br />\n**最後 200 張預售票熱賣中<br />\n<br />\n購票程序：<br />\n1. ATM 或 ebanking 轉帳票款到下列帳號：<br />\nHANG SENG BANK<br />\nBlack Market Music Production<br />\n224-443382-883<br />\n<br />\n2. 拍照入數紙 / 截圖轉帳紀錄，私信上傳到 黑市音樂 專頁，並留下一位聯絡人名字與電話號碼，稍候專人回覆確認便可。<br />\n<br />\n3. 演出當天核對名字與電話號碼換取門票進場。<br />\n<br />\n到時見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔係打手係粉絲"},{"pid":"8ea303f55e409b4982f0ce5071db5fdb49dd5f67","tid":920392,"uid":192257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T18:10:37.000Z","msg":"就到啦22號"},{"pid":"9f27d1e64dd355282208a612f2317ce03e3d8af7","tid":920392,"uid":18216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T11:07:40.000Z","msg":"有無人夾份買"},{"pid":"37554132d33af33d0f84d4fb60de6317d45bfad9","tid":920392,"uid":192257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T07:32:35.000Z","msg":"我多左張飛有冇人想要？"},{"pid":"d0a2272d88d004f8f6795cce8c64700530074026","tid":920392,"uid":18216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37554132d33af33d0f84d4fb60de6317d45bfad9","tid":920392,"uid":192257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T07:32:35.000Z","msg":"我多左張飛有冇人想要？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T13:00:11.000Z","msg":"咩價位"},{"pid":"1eb31d645f7662ee932548bd8c4b57e3e0292033","tid":920392,"uid":192257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0a2272d88d004f8f6795cce8c64700530074026","tid":920392,"uid":18216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37554132d33af33d0f84d4fb60de6317d45bfad9","tid":920392,"uid":192257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T07:32:35.000Z","msg":"我多左張飛有冇人想要？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T13:00:11.000Z","msg":"咩價位"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T14:01:29.000Z","msg":"好似太遲 係free"},{"pid":"632c9a9400260ebe320cf905323404d945848775","tid":920392,"uid":181988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T14:03:32.000Z","msg":"有無人今晚去咗?"},{"pid":"51363a2ea7cfc7c1a7d5e4d6a333590dfc80f992","tid":920392,"uid":18216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1eb31d645f7662ee932548bd8c4b57e3e0292033","tid":920392,"uid":192257,"like":0,"dislike":0